ize=1> Thanks NightGod!  I appreciate the response. I figured it was something like that. I plan to start the smithing tonight, so it should be interesting. We'll see how lucky I am.  I failed on a trivial Velium Vapor potion just yesterday so who knows!<br>
<br>
Smithing at 176. Everyone seems to think that it is all trivial now at 175 or so...but there's still that chance!  I have 6 star metals to work on, but only one chronium since it's lore.  I have my staff, luckily.<br>
<br>
Grundo is not to be taken lightly, by the way. He hits about like one of the regular giants, but he has a whole lot more hit pts.  So don't be fooled.  He's tough to bring down. With a druid to snare and DoT though, he went down without much trouble.<br>
<br>
Good luck!<br>
